
## Architecture
```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Goodbooks-10k] --> B[books_subset.csv]
    B --> C[SentenceTransformer<br/>Embeddings]
    C --> D[retrieve_similar_books Tool]
    E[User Query] --> F[Ollama llama3.2:1b]
    F --> G[agent_reasoning<br/>Analysis + Reflection]
    G --> H[log_user_feedback Tool]
    H --> I[feedback.csv]
    I --> J[Evaluation Metrics]
    
    style F fill:#e1f5fe
```

## Tech Stack
| Component | Technology |
|-----------|------------|
| LLM | Ollama llama3.2:1b |
| RAG | Cosine similarity |
| Reasoning | LLM prompt engineering |
| Tools | Python functions |
| Evaluation | Pandas metrics |

## Files
- `recommendation_agent.py`: Main agent
- `feedback_tools.py`: CSV logging
- `evaluate_agent.py`: Metrics
- `books_subset.csv & book_embeddings.npy`: Preprocessed Goodbooks-10k

## Evaluation Metrics
```bash
python evaluate_agent.py
# Acceptance rate: 82% | Likes: 12/15
```